cing-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{short description|South Korean fencer}}\n{{use dmy dates|date=August 2014}}\n{{Infobox sportsperson\n| name           = Lee Keum-nam\n| image          = \n| caption        = \n| birth_name     = \n| fullname       = \n| nickname       = \n| nationality    = \n| residence      = \n| birth_date     = {{birth date and age|1976|9|4|df=yes}}\n| birth_place    = \n| death_date     = \n| death_place    = \n| height         = \n| weight         = \n| website        = \n| country        = \n| sport          = [[Fencing]]\n| event          = \n| collegeteam    = \n| club           = \n| team           = \n| turnedpro      = \n| coach          = \n| retired        = \n| coaching       = \n| worlds         = \n| regionals      = \n| nationals      = \n| olympics       = \n| highestranking = \n| pb             = \n| show-medals    = yes\n}}\n\n'''Lee Keum-nam''' (born 4 September 1976) is a South Korean [[fencing|fencer]]. She competed in the [[\u00e9p\u00e9e]] events at the [[1996 Summer Olympics|1996]] and [[2004 Summer Olympics]].<ref name=\"sports-reference\">{{cite web |url=https://www.sports-reference.com/olympics/athletes/le/lee-geum-nam-1.html |title=Lee Geum-Nam Olympic Results |accessdate=2012-02-19 |work=sports-reference.com}}</ref>\n\n==References==\n{{reflist}}\n\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Lee, Keum-nam}}\n[[Category:1976 births]]\n[[Category:Living people]]\n[[Category:South Korean female fencers]]\n[[Category:Olympic fencers of South Korea]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 1996 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 2004 Summer Olympics]]\n[[Category:Asian Games medalists in fencing]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 1998 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Fencers at the 2002 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Asian Games gold medalists for South Korea]]\n[[Category:Asian Games silver medalists for South Korea]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 1998 Asian Games]]\n[[Category:Medalists at the 2002 Asian Games]]\n{{SouthKorea-fencing-bio-stub}}\